# 🎵 Music Player

A modern and responsive Music Player built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**. This application allows users to play, pause, skip, and navigate through a playlist with a clean and interactive user interface.

<p align="center">
  <img src="music_player_img.png" alt="Music Player Preview" width="800">
</p>

---

## ✨ Features

🎶 Play and pause songs  
⏭️ Next and previous song controls  
📃 Interactive playlist  
🎵 Displays current song title and artist  
📱 Responsive design for desktop and mobile devices  
🎨 Clean and modern user interface  
♿ Accessibility support with ARIA labels  

