---

## 🎮 Controls

| Button | Function |
|---------|-----------|
| ▶️ Play | Play the current song |
| ⏸️ Pause | Pause the current song |
| ⏮️ Previous | Play previous song |
| ⏭️ Next | Play next song |
| Playlist Item | Play selected song |

---

## 📱 Responsive Design

The application is fully responsive and works seamlessly on:

- 💻 Desktop
- 📱 Mobile
- 📟 Tablets

